data.description:
This beautiful corner lot home is conveniently located north of Twin Falls within walking distance to Rock Creek Elementary and St. Luke's Hospital. This property has an open floor plan with 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, and a decent size bonus room that can be a 4th bedroom/office. This property was built in 2019. This home has a large backyard with a fully 6ft vinyl fenced for full privacy and full automatic pressurize sprinklers.

Renter is responsible for all unities (natural gas, electric, water and sewer, city) and landscaping upkeep. No pets, no smoking. 
1 year lease
